---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 60
By: Ibn 'Atâ’illâh
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Separation-Sin=God’s Mercy
---
Mayhap He opens to thee the door of obedience and does not open to thee the
door of acceptance; and mayhap He ordains for thee sin, and it is an occasion
for realization.
